title: Venmathi Venmathiye Song Lyrics Minnale
stanzas:
Venmathi venmathiye nillu
nee vanukka megathukka sollu

[Venmathi venmathiye nillu
nee vanukka megathukka sollu
vanam thaan unnudaiya
istham endraam
megathuku illai oru nashtam

unnai indrodu
naan marappene
naan marappenae
unnaala nenjil poothak kadhal
melum melum
thunban vendaam] (2)

Jannalin vali
vandhu vilundhadhu
minnalin oli
adhil therindhadhu
azhagu dhevathai
adhisaya mugamae

theepori ena
iru vizhigalum
theekuchchi ena
enai urasida
kodi pookkalaai
malarandhadhu manamae

aval azhagai paada
oru mozhi illaiye
alandhu paarka pala
vizhi illaiye

enna irundha podhum
aval enadhillaiye
marandhu po
en manamae.

Oh ho ho..
Venmathi venmathiye nillu
nee vanukka megathukka sollu
vanam thaan unnudaiya
istham endraam
megathuku illai oru nashtam

unnai indrodu
naan marappene
naan marappenae
unnaala nenjil poothak kadhal
melum melum thunban vendaam

Anju naal varai
aval pozhindhadhu
aasaiyin mazhai
adhil nenaindhadhu
nooru jenmangal
ninaivinil irukkum

aaru pol enthan naal
varum uyir urugiya
andhanaal sugam
adhai ninaikaiyil
rathanaalangal
raathiri vedikkum.

oru nimisham kooda
ennai piriyavillai
vivaram yedhum
aval ariyavillai

enna irundha podhum
aval enadhillaiye
marandhu po
en manamae.

unnai indrodu
naan marappene
naan marappenae
unnaala nenjil poothak kadhal
melum melum
thunban vendaam
